{
  "texts": [
    "Let δ = 0.01 and tsteps = 200.",
    "When tank is in filling state for 150 time-steps, Levelval 150 = Levelval 150 + (0.01 • 150).",
    "Our accumulated drift is now 1.5 mm.",
    "Next, let the tank be in draining state for the next 50time steps.",
    "Then, Levelval 50 = Levelval 50 + 0.01 • (150 + 50)."
  ]
}